        <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="https://www.creativepassport.net/"/>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Premium digital identity standard for creatives; a database which holds verified profile information - portfolios, blogs, IDs, representatives, photo press kits, business partners and payment mechanisms, it helps get creatives and their works, linked and open (data) for business</skos:definition>
